content.text: table is designed to store temporary budget data for various agencies. It captures budgetary allocations or expenditures across different months of a fiscal year. The table includes columns for categorizing the data, identifying the fiscal year, versioning, and associating the data with specific budget and agency codes. Each month from July to June is represented as a separate column, allowing for detailed monthly financial tracking.
